Package gamePackage

Class Crop

java.lang.Object
gamePackage.Crop
public class Crop
extends java.lang.Object
Class Crop takes a String "crop" (e.g. "grass") that specified the crop to be created. Thus crop attributes are initialised through "crop". Has usual getters and setters for attributes purchasePrice, sellPrice, daysTillHarvest, cropAmount, cropType.
Author:
Swapnil Bhagat, Reed Earl
